adrive make drivers who use android navigation system(e.g: tmap4.0) get points by listening short sound based advertisement provided by nearby local business and driver can buy products by using their points . advertisers who provide these sound advertisement can promote their service or product and driver can save their assets easily, not spending their time unlike other reward platforms. we developed REST API server with php and codeigniter. and android application communicates with REST API server. the server developed with laravel manages advertisers and their advertise. prezi: http://prezi.com/poscej8ncm4d/adrive/?utm_campaign=share&utm_medium=copy Rest api server: http://54.251.110.67/ Admin server http://54.251.110.67:8080/
